About
=====

This INSTALL file is for cross-compiling Windows builds on Linux.

Tools
=====

g++, qt libs, ld, cmake and other utilities from the build-essential package.
mingw32 and windows contribs.

Building
========

Goto the source folder and do:
  mkdir win32 && cd win32
  cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=cmake/toolchain-win32.cmake ..
  make

Packaging
=========

To build the Null Soft Installer, do:
  make installer
